          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 2 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_3923218312422088833.png",
                "id": "talent19283",
                "key": "Plama Lawa",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Plama Lawa"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/b81f8bd6ae1e5b5f53807a4cd0704469_5701216531533229674.png",
                "id": "talent43068",
                "key": "Movo Lawa",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Movo Lawa"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 5 poin<span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/36768cf2c0fc7aafe7c6c956fee29fba_2829954124320504139.png",
                "id": "talent43622",
                "key": "Upa Shato",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "geo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Upa Shato"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Pasif) Saat pertandingan dimulai, Karakter ini memperoleh <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Infused Stonehide</span> dan <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Stone Force</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Infused Stonehide</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh menerima DMG:</span> Mengurangi 1 poin DMG yang diterima. Saat Geo DMG berkurang, mengonsumsi sekali lagi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> tambahan.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan: 3</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Stone Force</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> yang diakibatkan Karakter ini diubah menjadi <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo DMG</span>.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Sekali setiap Ronde:</span> Karakter mengakibatkan +1 DMG.</p><p>Setelah \"Infused Stonehide\" yang memberikan pengaruh pada Karakter dihapus, maka status ini juga akan dihapus.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/370c275e0af4838e7689aa8e24bc36c7_6988412038280111255.png",
                "id": "talent23300",
                "key": "Infused Stonehide",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Infused Stonehide"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Bereaksi dengan Elemen jika sudah diberikan:<br>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Cryo Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Hydro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Pyro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 230, 153)\">Geo</span> + <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro Crystallize</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, Karakter aktifmu memperoleh 1 poin Perisai (Dapat ditumpuk, maksimum 2 poin)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2022/12/06/1023623/fd37cbfdd3b1b2c16e6e83fb0aa96889_246359394830194740.png",
                "id": "talent79266",
                "key": "Geo DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Geo DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong></p><p>Physical DMG tidak dapat memberikan elemen apa pun dan memicu Reaksi Elemental.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Penggunaan</span></strong></p><p>Setelah efek kartu ini dipicu, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span>-nya akan dikonsumsi.</p><p>Kartu ini akan langsung dibuang setelah semua <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Penggunaan</span> telah dikonsumsi.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/03/04/25750596/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3094332428485469484.png",
